Name: Logic - Keypad
About the game: Puzzle game with numbers. Observe, find and combine clues to open doors. No horror. No storyline. Just Logic! This is my first personal game on Steam. I hope you enjoy it. You need to know some basic English words, search google, use calculator. - Zero, one, two, three... ten. Cat, dog, chicken... - 1+1=2, 550/2= ̶2̶̶2̶̶5̶ 275, 7568/86=88... Warning! The game is not for relaxation. This game is only for people who love challenging puzzle genres. You should consider trying the Demo version. I don't think it's suitable for everyone.
